1 (b) Is at least eighteen (18) years of age on or before the next regular election.
2 (11) For any operator's license or personal identification card issued by a local
3 official or local governmental entity under Section 1 of this Act, the local official
4 or local governmental entity may charge a convenience fee to be retained by the
5 local official or local governmental entity.
6 Section 3. This Act takes effect July 1, 2027.
